body:
{{item:3812}} 

I don&#039;t think it should interfere with any channeling longer than the 3 seconds. It&#039;s especially troublesome when you had a DoT on you. If a special rule could be made so Recall (and any other 3+ second channels interrupted by damage) is not cancelled by its delayed damage, that would be great.

That is all, thank you for your time.
